overview: Surrounded by men, Nikita is interested in and exchanges with them about masculinity and its stereotypes. After the departure of their friends, Nikita initiates Francois Sagat, an icon of gay cinema, in his first heterosexual situation in front of a camera. But Nikita's fans know that she likes to vary the pleasures: a naughty game between couples, a torrid masturbation or a perverse embrace between women in front of her man.
title: Obsessions 14
